# Group Jobs
Welcome to the jobs API. This API provides access to the jobs service.

## jobs [/jobs]

### Create job [POST]

Create a new job

+ Request jobs (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.apig+json
    + Attributes

        + user_id: 1 (number)
        + user ()
        + company_id: 1 (number)
        + role_cd: 1 (number)

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (jobs)

### Get jobs [GET]

Returns job list.

+ Request jobs (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.apig+json

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (array, fixed)
        + (jobs)

## job details [/jobs/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: `1` (enum[string]) - The ID of the desired job.
        + Members
            + `1`
            + `2`
            + `3`

### Get job [GET]

Returns job.

+ Request jobs (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.apig+json

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (jobs, fixed)

### Update job [PUT]

Update job.

+ Request jobs (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.apig+json
    + Attributes

        + user_id: 1 (number)
        + user ()
        + company_id: 1 (number)
        + role_cd: 1 (number)

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (jobs)

### Delete job [DELETE]

Delete job.

+ Request jobs (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.apig+json

+ Response 204

# Data Structures
## jobs (object, fixed)

+ id: 1 (number)
+ user_id: 1 (number)
+ user ()
+ company_id: 1 (number)
+ role_cd: 1 (number)
